{"TopicId":222698,"ForumId":39,"TopicTitle":"KSP Controller with 3DOF Docking control","CreatedByName":"mech_engr","CreatedById":117187,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-01-06T19:13:00Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"mech_engr","CreatedById":117187,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-01-06T19:13:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBuilt this controller last year for KSP2 and was super disappointed when controller support was nerfed. However, thanks to mods (\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/Codenade/ksp2-inputbinder/blob/master/README.md\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EInputBinder\u003C/a\u003E), I can finally play around with it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt was inspired by actual spacecraft docking controls, but I wanted a small gamepad-style controller.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe translation, or docking, handle on the left-hand side moves forward, backward, left, right, upwards, and downwards. It took a lot of prototyping to get to work correctly...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe joystick on the right is a standard analog joystick with 3 axes: pitch, roll, and yaw.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022113\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/yWSMqla8nWk?feature=oembed\u0022 title=\u0022KSP2 3DOF Docking Controller\u0022 width=\u0022200\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf there\u0027s enough support, I could publish the plans and bill of materials. I estimate it\u0027s about $50 to build.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cu\u003EConstruction:\u003C/u\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n3D printed housing\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nArduino Pro Micro\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nCustom code library for USB devices\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nStandard analog joystick\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n2 x analog sliders\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n3 x toggle switches\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n2 x square push buttons\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n1 x round, recessed, push button\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n1 x custom 3DOF docking stick\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n6 x microswitches\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n2 x springs\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nPlunger-handle\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n2 x pencil springs to center Z axis\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022PRub1Tv.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022166.67\u0022 height=\u0022900\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/PRub1Tv.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022wDKohir.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022166.67\u0022 height=\u0022900\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/wDKohir.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022U1QBMHn.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022166.67\u0022 height=\u0022900\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/U1QBMHn.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022jZuKnMA.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022166.67\u0022 height=\u0022900\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/jZuKnMA.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022PIIRLHR.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022166.67\u0022 height=\u0022900\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/PIIRLHR.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022oO3uujf.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022166.67\u0022 height=\u0022900\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/oO3uujf.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022ZLoUVHx.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022166.67\u0022 height=\u0022900\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/ZLoUVHx.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022yBqynDJ.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022166.67\u0022 height=\u0022900\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/yBqynDJ.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022jJNyaPF.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022166.67\u0022 height=\u0022900\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/jJNyaPF.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022UNtQdig.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022166.67\u0022 height=\u0022900\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/UNtQdig.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u002221bkOxc.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022166.67\u0022 height=\u0022900\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/21bkOxc.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022iXvLSZw.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022166.67\u0022 height=\u0022900\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/iXvLSZw.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLots of painful prototyping........\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00225tDWcGh.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022166.67\u0022 height=\u00221200\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/5tDWcGh.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is the translation controller on the latest Boeing capsule. I believe it also rotates for attitude control making it 6DOF.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022rQXjF92.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022130.19\u0022 height=\u00221078\u0022 width=\u0022828\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/rQXjF92.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheSpaceDinos4037","CreatedById":229961,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-01-07T21:08:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDude, this is amazing! Would love to see this on sale like the control panel keyboards.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"gillou","CreatedById":232124,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-01-09T17:10:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nC\u0027est vraiment top bravo.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIl y a moyen d\u0027avoir ou t\u0027acheter \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Launch Escape System\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Launch Escape System\u0022\u003Eles\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E plans et la liste des composants ?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u2019s really great, well done.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs there a way to get or buy\u00A0the\u00A0plans and the list of components?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222024-01-09T20:05:57Z\u0022 title=\u002201/09/2024 08:05  PM\u0022 data-short=\u0022Jan 9\u0022\u003EJanuary 9\u003C/time\u003E by Vanamonde\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EPlease post in English when not using the International subforums.\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AstroWolfie","CreatedById":223932,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-01-23T18:56:05Z","Con